{"tid":1228390,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"「聯署」要求英國廢除中英聯合聲明、褫奪高官英藉","createTime":"2019-06-15T16:58:19.000Z","updateTime":"2019-06-16T16:58:59.000Z","uid":227140,"like":22,"dislike":0,"uniUserReply":4,"replies":[{"pid":"ac6f8ecd25b0e4f937d1a94eef7b613c7e0d7fa1","tid":1228390,"uid":227140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T16:58:19.000Z","msg":"英國佬未必得閒理我地、亦未必會理我地，但係事已至此，冇成本既都做下啦<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/frown.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" /> <br />\n就算你可能會話香港應該自治、獨立，先歸英後獨立點都容易過你喺中共政權下獨立 <br />\n<br />\n同朋友DRAFT左個聯署，希望大家都去支持下 <br />\n<a href=\"http://chng.it/Hb52fZmjLH \" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=http%3A%2F%2Fchng.it%2FHb52fZmjLH%20&d=YAxVOUHAW5%2FtYfR1oVoe2%2FS0i%2BS8%2FYHgnNJfWlbrK%2Bw%3D&h=082d0100\" target=\"_blank\">http://chng.it/Hb52fZmjLH </a><br />\n<br />\n簡而言之係促請英政府廢取中英聯合聲明、收回香港主權、制裁支持逃犯引渡條例既主要官員、追究差佬濫用武力、撒銷所有暴動罪指控同釋放因該指控而受拘留人士"},{"pid":"79b90fe278028257c2ae852204f99cabaf208fb6","tid":1228390,"uid":52230,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:29:09.000Z","msg":"咪靠英狗啦屌"},{"pid":"e66ea056dfc8c022016cc663fe4d1060efbb0f37","tid":1228390,"uid":227140,"like":9,"dislike":0,"score":9,"quote":{"pid":"79b90fe278028257c2ae852204f99cabaf208fb6","tid":1228390,"uid":52230,"like":8,"dislike":2,"score":6,"citedBy":1,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:29:09.000Z","msg":"咪靠英狗啦屌"},"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-15T17:34:43.000Z","msg":"我唔會叫大家坐喺屋企咩都唔做等英國佬救，當年有心既唔會拱手相讓、今時今日英國佬自身難保亦唔荒會出幫，但係我認為我地起碼應該要出聲"},{"pid":"27531404675dc6e5c8998772691d7a0324763a8b","tid":1228390,"uid":227140,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T02:41:07.000Z","msg":"希望大家行街前睇睇<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/smile.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"32f7936bb7fb22e91fa8f89c3e6dd5609e9504c5","tid":1228390,"uid":227769,"like":1,"dislike":0,"score":1,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:50:51.000Z","msg":"【聯署】要求英國當局撤銷林鄭老公同兩個仔ge英國國籍<br />\n- 分享自 LIHKG 討論區<br />\n<a href=\"https://lih.kg/cPdzNS\" data-auto-link target=\"_blank\">https://lih.kg/cPdzNS</a><br />\n<br />\n相關聯署"},{"pid":"63409c57e863c612c255d8b001190bbc4a89cfe5","tid":1228390,"uid":52960,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2019-06-16T16:58:59.000Z","msg":"英國佬近排都好唔得閑，收回香港近乎零。<br />\n中港融合咗多年，人種文化制度都係劣化中。有咩着數俾英國佬？"}]}